# Fruit Shop — Microservices Stack

เปิดด้วย `fruit-shop.code-workspace` (multi-root) — มี 5 repos ทำงานร่วมกัน

## Architecture

```
Frontend (:5173)  fruit-shop-frontend
  └── API Gateway (:3004)  Api-Gateway
        ├── Auth Service (:3100)        Auth-Service      → /auth/*
        ├── Commerce API (:3000)          commerce-api      → /products, /cart, /orders, /payments
        └── Notification Service (:3001)  notification-service → /notifications/*
              MongoDB (:27017) — shared database
```

## Repositories

| Folder | Port | Role |
|--------|------|------|
| `fruit-shop-frontend` | 5173 | React + Vite, เรียก Gateway |
| `Api-Gateway` | 3004 | Proxy + JWT guard |
| `commerce-api` | 3000 | Products, cart, orders, Omise payments |
| `Auth-Service` | 3100 | Register, login, JWT refresh |
| `notification-service` | 3001 | In-app notifications |

## Shared secrets (ต้องตรงกันทุก service)

- `JWT_SECRET` — Auth, Commerce, Notification
- `MONGODB_URI` / `MONGO_URI` — Auth, Commerce, Notification (notification ใช้ชื่อ `MONGO_URI`)

## Local setup

```bash
# จาก commerce-api repo
chmod +x scripts/setup-workspace.sh
./scripts/setup-workspace.sh ~/fruit-shop
# เปิด ~/fruit-shop/fruit-shop.code-workspace ใน Cursor Desktop
# Run Task: 🚀 Start All Services
```

## Gateway env keys

- `AUTH_SERVICE_URL` → `http://localhost:3100`
- `COMMERCE_API_URL` → `http://localhost:3000` (ไม่ใช่ COMMERCE_SERVICE_URL)
- `NOTIFICATION_SERVICE_URL` → `http://localhost:3001`

## Payment flow

Checkout → PENDING order → Omise charge → PAID → clear cart → notification `payment_success`
